column5: Is that a joke or what does that do?

Did you get a feeling sort of like you’re hopped up on caffeine and dead tired at the same time? I don’t always get it with high doses of shrooms but it happens for me every time I take more than ~250ug of acid.

I haven’t personally used it but I have heard of a lot of people using it. Most seem to have good luck with it from what I’ve heard. When I was researching what to use myself I came across the same issue of finding shady shit on different products and honestly I dont think that a lot of it is founded by any real evidence. Like how people knock PG even though it’s been used in vapes since like 2013. I still wouldn’t use that for carts cuz it doesn’t mix well but it’s still a perfectly good alternative that people seem to think will kill you or something. People like to have opinions lol
Pyur is a perfectly fine brand to use. Really as long as there isn’t too much shit that comes up when you google the brand you should be fine.
You can use either, but if you’re going to do it right use terpines. I used propylene glycol to make some carts and it turned out ok but from experience terps just are better overall

I think a lot of your trip is what you expect it to be honestly. When I first started psychedelics I did not really know that bad/scary trips were a thing that happened and I can guarantee that helped with my experiences. Most of the people I know (including me) haven’t really ever had a bad trip. Acid has always been a super fun substance for me to be on. With how much it lifts my mood, I don’t see a bad trip happening for me in the future either. I’ve had experiences where the trip hasn’t been fun, but never mind bogglingly terrifying.
